{
  "$schema": "https://vega.github.io/schema/vega-lite/v5.json",
  "description": "Earnings Data from UK Parliament: Average earnings by age and region (November 2021). I downloaded the Excel workbook, extracted the appropriate data and transformed it. Cost of Living data from MoneyNest: Cost of Living analysis 2019. I scraped this data using Python, created a pandas dataframe, exported to CSV and combined with the earnings data. I uploaded this CSV to Github and used the raw link as the data source for this chart. All data sources and workings are linked below this chart.",
